fullplot: Interviews, archival footage and home movies are used to illustrate a social history of folk artist and activist Pete Seeger.
plot: Interviews, archival footage and home movies are used to illustrate a social history of folk artist and activist Pete Seeger.
title: Pete Seeger: The Power of Song

tomatoes.consensus: Pete Seeger: The Power of Song is both a tribute to a legendary singer and an informative account of the birth of American counterculture.
